## What is current

Current scripts:

- `scripts/backfill_atproto_posts.py`
- `scripts/live_collect_atproto_posts.py`
- `scripts/build_seed_author_list.py`
- `scripts/backfill_seed_authors.py`
- `scripts/live_collect_seed_authors.py`
- `scripts/export_strict_sl_corpus.py`
- `scripts/sample_main_corpus.py`

